ink":"https://www.ifanr.com/1655944?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-27 10:40:21","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f9f5c72b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_4635d3ac","title":"使用 fetch() HTTP Range 请求进行二分搜索的 Unicode 浏览器","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Feb/27/unicode-explorer/#atom-everything","date":"2026-02-27 17:50:54","oneSentenceSummary":"本文展示了一个技术原型，通过 HTTP Range 请求对大型远程文件进行高效的二分搜索，并强调了如压缩兼容性等具体的实现挑战。","summary":"Simon Willison 通过构建一个 Unicode 浏览器探索了 HTTP Range 请求的实际应用。该工具针对托管在 S3 上的 76.6MB 元数据文件执行二分搜索，允许浏览器在不下载整个数据集的情况下检索特定字符信息。文章详细介绍了使用 Claude 和 Claude Code 从概念构思到功能原型的开发流程。一个关键的技术收获是发现 Range 请求与 HTTP 压缩不兼容，因为压缩会改变字节偏移量，这需要使用 “identity” 编码或 CDN 级别的绕过。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4635d3ac.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":2,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_43438ea0","title":"何恺明团队新作 GeoPT，全新预训练范式让模型自学真实物理规律","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/382888.html","date":"2026-02-27 08:19:25","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_43438ea0.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_42ce8ee4","title":"杀进全球榜 TOP2！国产视频模型黑马刚刚出现了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/382803.html","date":"2026-02-27 08:04:54","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_42ce8ee4.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_3ce9568f","title":"囤积你已知如何实现的东西 —— 智能体工程模式","link":"https://simonwillison.net/guides/agentic-engineering-patterns/hoard-things-you-know-how-to-do/#atom-everything","date":"2026-02-26 20:33:27","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3ce9568f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_35edc300","title":"CORPGEN 推动 AI 智能体处理真实工作","link":"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/corpgen-advances-ai-agents-for-real-work/","date":"2026-02-26 17:10:15","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_35edc300.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Microsoft Research Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_3308e250","title":"智谱 GLM-5 技术全公开！完全适配华为等国产芯片，美国网友酸了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/381712.html","date":"2026-02-23 05:19:44","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3308e250.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_f6110ead","title":"MySQL 9.6 变更外键约束与级联处理机制","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/mysql-foreign-keys/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-28 08:34:00","oneSentenceSummary":"MySQL 9.6 将外键和级联管理从 InnoDB 引擎移至 SQL 层，确保这些操作最终能被记录在二进制日志中，从而实现可靠的 CDC 和复制。","summary":"本文详细介绍了 MySQL 9.6 在外键（FK）约束方面的重大架构转变。历史上，InnoDB 在内部处理外键验证和级联，这意味着这些变更从未记录在二进制日志中，常导致下游系统出现数据漂移。通过将此逻辑移至 SQL 层，MySQL 9.6 确保了变更数据捕获（CDC）流水线和分析平台的完全可见性。尽管 Oracle 报告称其性能与旧方法持平，但社区对缺乏官方文档以及 Oracle 领导下 MySQL 开发路线图的透明度表示担忧。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f6110ead.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":78},{"id":"RAW_c50842ba","title":"Storyteller：一种引导他人理解代码的新媒介","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/storyteller-a-medium-for-guiding-others-through-code/","date":"2026-02-28 01:07:32","oneSentenceSummary":"本文介绍了 Storyteller，这是一款通过创建交互式代码回放来弥补静态博客文章与线性视频教程之间差距的技术教育工具。","summary":"作者是一位计算机科学讲师，他指出了传统学习格式的局限性：书籍内容过于密集，博客割裂了代码上下文，而视频则难以搜索或控制进度。为了解决这些问题，他开发了 Storyteller，这是一个 VS Code 插件，可以记录代码的演变过程，并允许作者嵌入文本、绘图和音频等丰富的注释。这些“回放”托管在 Playback Press 上，提供了一个可搜索、交互式的环境，学习者可以在代码和博客视图之间切换。此外，作者还集成了一个具备上下文感知能力的 AI 导师，它能理解代码回放的具体状态，从而回答学生的问题并生成自动评分的测验，旨在模拟专家引导的讲解体验。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c50842ba.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_03c4951e","title":"从“凭感觉测试”到持续评估：构建可靠的 AI 智能体","link":"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/from-vibe-checks-to-continuous-evaluation-engineering-reliable-ai-agents/","date":"2026-02-28 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_03c4951e.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Google Cloud Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_8589d9ac","title":"深入了解 Eventarc Advanced","link":"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/application-modernization/getting-to-know-eventarc-advanced/","date":"2026-02-28 00:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Eventarc Advanced 引入了“集中式策略，分布式逻辑”架构，将治理（总线）与集成逻辑（流水线）解耦，以平衡组织控制与开发者的敏捷性。","summary":"本文探讨了集成架构的演进，从企业服务总线（ESB）的集中式瓶颈到现代微服务中的治理鸿沟。文章介绍了 Eventarc Advanced 这一无服务器解决方案，旨在解决这种矛盾。通过将“总线”（Bus，用于 SecOps 执行安全和数据策略的集中治理层）与“流水线”（Pipeline，用于开发者处理转换和路由的分布式逻辑层）分离，它实现了安全、自主的事件驱动开发。文章通过零售事件网格示例详细介绍了实际应用，展示了 CloudEvents、通用表达式语言（CEL）以及 Agent2Agent (A2A) 等协议如何在无需集中式中间件干预的情况下，促进模式感知的转换和 AI 智能体的编排。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8589d9ac.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Google Cloud Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_6c861597","title":"使用 Google Cloud 提升聊天机器人记忆能力","link":"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/improve-chatbot-memory-using-google-cloud/","date":"2026-02-28 00:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文介绍了一种基于 Google Cloud 的分层多语言存储架构，利用 Redis、Bigtable 和 BigQuery 管理 AI 聊天机器人在不同时间尺度上的记忆。","summary":"本文通过提出一种稳健的分层数据层架构，解决了扩展对话式 AI 智能体的关键挑战。它提倡一种“多语言”存储方法，根据数据的“温度”和生命周期选择不同的技术。对于短期“热”上下文，Memorystore for Redis 提供亚毫秒级延迟，利用 Redis Lists 和 RPUSH 命令避免低效的“读取-修改-写入”循环。随着对话的进行，Cloud Bigtable 作为 PB 级的中期历史记录系统，采用专门的行键策略（user_id#session_id#reverse_timestamp）以确保快速的范围扫描和会话检索。对于长期归档和深度商业智能，数据被移动到 BigQuery，从而在不影响实时性能的情况下实现复杂的 SQL 分析和模型优化反馈循环。此外，该架构通过指针策略使用 Cloud Storage 存储多媒体工件，并利用 Pub/Sub 和 Dataflow 构建混合同步-异步流水线，以平衡即时响应能力与长期数据持久性。这一综合框架确保了为数百万用户提供服务的智能体的对话连续性和可扩展性，同时保持了完整且可搜索的交互历史。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6c861597.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Google Cloud Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_5bae7b12","title":"从创意到 Pull Request：使用 GitHub Copilot CLI 构建项目的实用指南","link":"https://github.blog/ai-and-ml/github-copilot/from-idea-to-pull-request-a-practical-guide-to-building-with-github-copilot-cli/","date":"2026-02-27 16:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5bae7b12.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The GitHub Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_bd73dacd","title":"有毒组合：当微小信号汇聚成安全事件","link":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/toxic-combinations-security/","date":"2026-02-27 15:00:08","oneSentenceSummary":"本文介绍了“有毒组合”的概念——即多个微小的安全信号汇聚在一起预示着严重的违规行为——并提供了数据驱动的检测和缓解策略。","summary":"Cloudflare 探讨了一种名为“有毒组合”的高级安全框架，该框架将重点从单个请求分析转向上下文关联检测。通过分析机器人活动、敏感应用路径、请求异常和错误配置的交集，安全团队可以识别出缺乏明显攻击特征的潜在事件。文章详细介绍了在 Cloudflare 网络中发现的五种常见场景：管理端点的探测、通过可预测 ID 导致的未授权 API 数据泄露、调试参数泄漏、暴露的监控端点以及成功的 SQL 注入尝试。针对每种场景，作者提供了用于日志分析的特定类 SQL 查询，解释了潜在的业务风险，并提供了从实施零信任（Zero Trust）到边缘级参数过滤的可操作缓解步骤。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bd73dacd.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Cloudflare Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_e440d9a8","title":"Vercel 发布 React 最佳实践技能，包含 40 多条面向 AI 智能体的性能规则","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/vercel-react-best-practices/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-27 14:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_e440d9a8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Program