","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo6Gtq3nMXc","date":"2026-02-23 20:43:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ab2f755.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Pragmatic Engineer","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":32,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_64fc2a7","title":"Builders Unscripted：第 1 集 - OpenClaw 创始人 Peter Steinberger","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9jgcT0Fqt7U","date":"2026-02-24 17:03:32","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_64fc2a7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"OpenAI","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":37,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_8d728e4","title":"#434.AI 时代的生存法则：纳瓦尔谈氛围编程、个人杠杆与创造力的未来","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/699dec62de29766da968a099","date":"2026-02-24 23:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8d728e4.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"跨国串门儿计划","resourceType":"PODCAST","readTime":7,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_2027057726170509724","title":"谷歌发布 Nano Banana 2：集成实时联网功能的超高保真图像模型","link":"https://x.com/sundarpichai/status/2027057726170509724","date":"2026-02-26 16:26:37","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2027057726170509724.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Sundar Pichai(@sundarpichai)","resourceType":"TWITTER","readTime":3,"score":94}]
